      • testBasicBehavior

        public void testBasicBehavior()
                       throws Exception
        test basic behavior with simple input. expectations:
        • reads decoded (uncompressed) contents from archive record.
        • calls delegator.handleParseStart() and handleParseComplete() just once, respectively.
        • calls HttpServletResponse.setHeader() for Content-Type, Content-Length and TextReplayRenderer.GUESSED_CHARSET_HEADER (not configurable as with TextReplayRenderer subclasses.
        • calls HttpServletResponse.setCharsetEncoding() with value "utf-8"
        • passes CaptureSearchResult.originalUrl to ParseContext.baseUrl
        URL translation is not tested here because it is not a responsibility of this class. it should be tested in a test case for ParseEventHandler implementations.
        Throws:
        Exception
